{"tid":2016881,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Lisa當練習生初期「每天打給媽媽哭」　曝BLACKPINK同居10年相處內幕","createTime":"2020-05-14T17:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T06:05:22.000Z","uid":74065,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d39f2d4a7322996cc1e14d2a15acfc50e6ccf89b","tid":2016881,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:37:19.000Z","msg":"南韓女團「BLACKPINK」的泰籍成員Lisa長相甜美，被封為「人間芭比」。她近期在大陸選秀節目《青春有你2》擔任導師，就以自身經歷分享練習生時期的血淚史，更分享團員之間的相處故事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4877/d4877915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4877%2Fd4877915.jpg&h=63329b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa為「BLACKPINK」成員。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／Lisa）<br />\n<br />\nLisa當練習生剛開始的三個月，一直打電話給媽媽哭訴，那之後就好多了，能夠更快的調整自己，「只要有人在支持我們，我們就一定能跨過艱難和困苦。」她也以自身經驗鼓勵在場的訓練生們，「你覺得累，可以哭出來，可以收拾好自己的情緒，希望大家可以繼續進步不放棄。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4877/d4877912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4877%2Fd4877912.jpg&h=69f79269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa曝練習生時期心酸。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n聊到團員時，Lisa表示BLACKPINK4人已經在一起生活十年了，她透露當團裡有人心情低落時，大家就會一起去吃大餐紓壓，而身為隊裡年紀最小的她，也常受到另外三位成員的照顧，她透露一開始去韓國當練習生時，自己的韓文不好，有一位成員一直帶著她去吃飯、去旅遊，讓她的韓文進步神速，她更特別感謝對方：「如果沒有她，我的韓文也不會說得這麼好。」可見BLACKPINK之間的好感情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4877/d4877913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4877%2Fd4877913.jpg&h=a55d92f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4877/d4877914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4877%2Fd4877914.jpg&h=af989bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa分享BLACKPINK團員感情、生活。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\nJISOO我女友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9622d03b23fcb48996fbb05b1f9178417165f7","tid":2016881,"uid":125502,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"26064194f43b2b67083b16881b9a34c9429c3d29","tid":2016881,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇新一集先睇到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508a14ed555df32d1efd128e8b6079dac054eda3","tid":2016881,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T17:40:27.000Z","msg":"痴線呢個年代仲體罰?"},{"pid":"abe5cbf65d18f7965a7e642e076602098bf8634e","tid":2016881,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T18:34:53.000Z","msg":"最慘既LISA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17a5fdaead4bc82130d4d20b5436956ce7792d4","tid":2016881,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"abe5cbf65d18f7965a7e642e076602098bf8634e","tid":2016881,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T18:34:53.000Z","msg":"最慘既LISA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T20:20:07.000Z","msg":"用力打，往死裡給我打"},{"pid":"3bc28b719f02474d890c7f4644c2b139e544c021","tid":2016881,"uid":40843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T22:07:12.000Z","msg":"睇左做每天給媽媽打"},{"pid":"a138fddadbf937fd803b5b60